title: Extinction AD - Plague Prophecy (EP)  mp3 CBR 256k a2k 2014
description:
Extinction AD - Plague Prophecy (EP)  mp3 CBR 256k a2k 2014 What we got...Good Fight Music welcomes Extinction A.D. to its expanding family and announces the August 19th release of the band's debut EP, "Plague Prophecy."

The EP was recorded, mixed, and mastered by Jay Maas at Getaway Recording (Defeater, Ceremony, Bane) and features cover art by U.K. artist Will Blood. The track listing is as follows:

1. Arsenal of Freedom
2. Doomsday Clock
3. Mummified
4. Extinction A.D.
